//orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569",{"_":196,"when":197,"who":181},"Jonathan Prag edited from published edition of ISegesta","2022-05-09",{"n":105,"url":106,"height":107,"width":108,"desc":109,"surfaceType":110},[200],{"atLeast":201,"atMost":202},40,56,[204,205,206],"Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Nenci, 1995, Iscrizioni greche e latine","Ampolo, Erdas, 2019, Inscriptiones Segestanae. Le iscrizioni greche e latine di Segesta",[208,209,210],"F2GG87EQ","WHBJDH75","3PK3JKXR",[212,213,214,23,29,33,215,215,216,217,215,218,219,137],"isic002729","i.sicily inscription 002729",{"_":5},"segesta","sicilia","sicily","parco archeologico di segesta","ancient greek",[],{"title":222,"body":223,"divs":224,"editions":249,"images":259,"handnote":265},"ISic002729. I.Sicily inscription 002729","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Π̣ΑΤΡ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>ἐ]κκ τῶν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].ΑΤΡ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΚΚΤΩΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002729_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002729_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002729.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002729-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after ISegesta G25\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Nenci: [---]ἰατρῶν; SEG after Nenci: [---]ἰατρ[ῶν]; Ampolo and Erdas note only a vertical stroke is visible at the start, but that more likely is e.g. [--Σώ]πατρ- vel sim.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Nenci suggested emending κκ in line 3 to ἐκ but Ampolo and Erdas note that gemination of the κ is well attested. Ampolo and Erdas suggest that the word ἰδίων may have stood in the first part of the line (4) below line 3, which is empty on the stone; but if the text extended onto a second stone, as is implied by line 2, then it could equally have followed on line 3. The proposed early imperial date is based solely on letter forms.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 45.1394 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Nenci 1995 1183 no.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G25 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-3  40-56  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[225,228,231,234,237,240,243,246],{"id":226,"html":227},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Π̣ΑΤΡ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>ἐ]κκ τῶν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].ΑΤΡ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΚΚΤΩΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":229,"html":230},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002729_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002729_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002729.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002729-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":232,"html":233},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after ISegesta G25\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Nenci: [---]ἰατρῶν; SEG after Nenci: [---]ἰατρ[ῶν]; Ampolo and Erdas note only a vertical stroke is visible at the start, but that more likely is e.g. [--Σώ]πατρ- vel sim.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":235,"html":236},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":238,"html":239},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Nenci suggested emending κκ in line 3 to ἐκ but Ampolo and Erdas note that gemination of the κ is well attested. Ampolo and Erdas suggest that the word ἰδίων may have stood in the first part of the line (4) below line 3, which is empty on the stone; but if the text extended onto a second stone, as is implied by line 2, then it could equally have followed on line 3. The proposed early imperial date is based solely on letter forms.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":241,"html":242},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 45.1394 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Nenci 1995 1183 no.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G25 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":244,"html":245},"handnote"," Line 1-3  40-56  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":247,"html":248},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[250,252,255,256],{"html":251},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag",{"id":253,"lang":137,"html":254},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Π̣ΑΤΡ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>ἐ]κκ τῶν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":251},{"id":257,"lang":137,"html":258},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].ΑΤΡ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan 